Robin!

193
00:08:49,895 --> 00:08:50,683
Robin!

194
00:08:51,518 --> 00:08:52,798
Ei, eu estou aqui.

195
00:08:54,867 --> 00:08:57,334
I-i-indo à Philly!

196
